            Lazio are not CL material - and their defence is a bit of a mystery against the top three Napoli/Roma/Juve. Juve - Malmo will be tough at home, so an eye on that. You can see Lazio scoring here, but Juve to end up 1-2 1-3. A draw would surprise because Lazio will have to be very tight as a unit - something they have not shown against smaller teams - so can they step up for this game? That is the unknown, but Juve should edge through.
